<br>
Lately, I have been having anxiety problems in large groups of people, and it really sucks at work.  I deliver pizza, and the dispatching area is quite tiny, maybe 10 feet long by 4 feet wide.  Entirely too small of a place for a few people to gather around.  This used to not bother me though, all the drivers could be standing around there all crammed up each others asses, and I wouldn't give a shit.  I've just been getting more paranoid of people, and more claustrophobic, more anti-social, more disgusted with some of these people the longer i work there.   One of the drivers, Lee, is a dirty old man, who makes sick perverted jokes, because he will <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>never</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> in his life feel the touch of a woman.  The man doesn't bathe, or brush his teeth, and he makes the sickest comments.  All the teens in the town I work in are spoiled ass brats, and 16 year old girls will be driving brand new Mustangs, Camaro's or whatever around.  I saw some 16 year old girl driving around a GEORGEOUS 1968 or so Corvette the other day.  So, I make an occasional joke about these girls flirting with their dads to get what they want...but...this louse takes it wrongly and says.. &quot;Well, if my daughter looked like that, I'd wanna fuck her too!&quot;  What the hell?!?!  That isn't funny in the slightest, this filthy ass shit.  I am completely ashamed to work around these people.  All in all, I find myself more disgusted with humanity every day, I work with the trashiest people you will find, stupid stoners, high school dropouts, my boss lost one of her eyes when she wrecked her car because she was coked up and drunk.  These people swarm around me every day, I get sick to my stomach because of it. These people have worked this job for years.  Anyone else here ever delivered pizza?? Well, you'd understand that it's a lousy job.  These people have it as a damn career.  Are your social skills that lousy that you can't find decent work?!  Are you such social misfits that you cant get up off your ass, and do something with your life?!  I'm only 22, and I'm sickened with myself over having this job for more than a year,I should be doing something decent.<br>
<br>
This anxiety thing just isn't at work, it's at parties, with groups of friends.  Almost anywhere other than a concert or rave.  I go the mall, and I am completely disgusted by people.  People that think that their life is so perfect because they're the star quarterback or head cheerleader at their school.<br>
<br>
I know some reasons why I have been having crazy ass mood swings, and this anxiety.  Poor diet, stressed out like hell, i need a change of job/apartment, I need a vacation.  But I don't know the definate root of it.  Am I sick of everyone else, or sick of myself?  Why did I think nice happy thoughts of blowing a rather large chunk out of my skull, while drving at the same time on the way home from work today?  What the hell is wrong with me?!  I don't know if I may have a chemical imbalance.  Possibly I do, I do all sorts of other weird shit, maybe it's just nervous ticks.<br>
<br>
I dunno...maybe I just have one hell of an ego and think I'm perfect.  Maybe I'm just hopeful that I will catch one small break, so I can get both feet on the ground, and I get pissed at others that are perfectly happy with wasting away.<br>
<br>
Ugh.<br>
<br>
Maybe I just need to go take a shower, listen to some Pink Floyd, and attempt to relax.<br>
<br>
Anyway, thanks for reading this.  I know not a single one of you knows me in real life.  And only a handful have spoken to me in game.  So feel free to call me a social fuckup if you wish, tell me I need to jump off a bridge, whatever.<br>
<br>
Later<br>
